item.title: [HIVE-20520] length(CHAR) doesn't consider trailing space
item.description:
Reproduce steps:

create table test(a char(2), b varchar(2));
insert into test values('L ', 'L ');
select length(a),length(b) from test;
+------+------+
| _c0  | _c1  |
+------+------+
| 1    | 2    |
+------+------+
1 row selected (0.185 seconds)

Here char with trailing spaces are trimmed, whereas leading spaces are not trimmed.

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
